{"tid":2457860,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟巨人世界d人忍痛能力有幾高？","createTime":"2021-03-23T03:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T18:14:43.000Z","uid":147737,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f41b3237e60097e67e6c8c2b6e60f7f56e8071ac","tid":2457860,"uid":147737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:44:06.000Z","msg":"普通人/要傳授巨人之力既人俾巨人食已經夠癲，但已經叫好啲，叫做真係死咗，一了百了<br />\n智慧巨人先恐怖，大家都知佢哋斷手斷腳係家常便飯，成世人都唔知斷幾多次。正常人斷一次應該都痛到失去知覺，佢哋仲要瘋狂斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變身又要介手又咬自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nZeke又係，一直都心諗佢啲脊髓液係咪無限供應，點解可以有咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多到俾成條村，成個軍團啲人飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算真係有咁多，提取嘅方法應該都痛到飛起，咁佢係咪真係要好定期咁抽取脊髓液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下都痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9f3645d807e96dc2535631837513689a33212f","tid":2457860,"uid":189417,"like":101,"dislike":14,"score":87,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"香港人忍痛能力都好高<br />\n出街隨時俾人打<br />\n就快俾人捉去打針<br />\n仍然堅持日常生活<br />\n唔助長負面情緒"},{"pid":"2034e2df6214e77d9506021c4d4084713d9a6767","tid":2457860,"uid":180124,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"火影果啲人可以自己攞兩隻手指挖自己隻眼出黎添"},{"pid":"694a38cf4ae5942e3d8ec6719ce149ed34075bec","tid":2457860,"uid":24512,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"2034e2df6214e77d9506021c4d4084713d9a6767","tid":2457860,"uid":180124,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"火影果啲人可以自己攞兩隻手指挖自己隻眼出黎添"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"再好似USB咁插入去用返"},{"pid":"e5e67a0273553e7a2fcce7976df264fcf7842935","tid":2457860,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"694a38cf4ae5942e3d8ec6719ce149ed34075bec","tid":2457860,"uid":24512,"like":57,"dislike":0,"scor